pull_request.title: Renaming nginx/fulltest-provider -> nginx/fulltest & delete old fulltest dir.
pull_request.body:
As suggested in https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/oqs-demos/pull/245#issuecomment-1792653164:

Deletes the old OpenSSL 1.1.1 nginx "fulltest" and renames the oqs-provider based "fulltest-provider" to "fulltest".

pull_request.title: Update test server generation/deployment scripts (libOQS 0.9.2)
pull_request.body:
- Update test server generation scripts to libOQS 0.9.2 & nginx 1.25.3
- Dockerfile provides option to re-use root CA if it already exists, adds note in README about this
- Adds HSTS to server config (satisfying a hosting security policy)
- Adds note about * designator in test server html (taken from PR #259 and adapted to the server config)

The new build is already deployed at test.openquantumsafe.org and the test run passes.

Fixes #256 
Fixes #253
